How to Install a WooCommerce Theme?

It takes a few steps to start working with a WooCommerce theme on your WordPress website. You should:

Go to Appearance > Themes.

Search for a free theme in the WordPress repository or upload the theme’s file.

Install and Activate the theme.

That’s it! Watch a detailed video tutorial on how to create an e-commerce website with WooCommerce.

